{"tid":1970062,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"上星期返工發生咗件怪事，搞到老婆黑咗我三日面......","createTime":"2020-04-13T00:38:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T11:53:13.000Z","uid":28938,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"41ac097bed3c5b07a9925d280bfb113b2abb3a53","tid":1970062,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T00:38:43.000Z","msg":"部門有個妹妹最近決定去外國進修所以遞咗信。<br />\n<br />\n星期四同佢食中午飯farewell 佢，佢堅持要我恤衫第二粒鈕做留念......<br />\n<br />\n返到去老婆洗衫，問我點解冇咗粒鈕，我就講返件事出嚟，點知佢一聽完就幾日都唔同我講嘢，黑面黑到我今朝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問佢咩事又唔肯講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"103d7b6c85c653538e2024d92bef1168a8b9981f","tid":1970062,"uid":40272,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T00:43:03.000Z","msg":"因為你唔大方 <br />\n正常人都成件衫比埋佢 <br />\n你老婆覺得好收家"},{"pid":"7cbe00f8390a5ed65f759b0c06594745acc54d9e","tid":1970062,"uid":41643,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T00:44:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E9%A1%86%E9%88%95%E9%87%A6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E9%25A1%2586%25E9%2588%2595%25E9%2587%25A6&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWYWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=41c99793\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E9%A1%86%E9%88%95%E9%87%A6</a><br />\n<br />\n第二顆鈕釦的文化源自日本，當女生在畢業典禮（卒業式）向男生索取校服上的第二顆鈕釦時，代表她喜歡對方，假使男方願意交出自己的第二顆鈕釦，即代表願意和對方正式交往。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19bd9a3b9c33091766c8427be8cca6a326909ba4","tid":1970062,"uid":316715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7cbe00f8390a5ed65f759b0c06594745acc54d9e","tid":1970062,"uid":41643,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T00:44:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E9%A1%86%E9%88%95%E9%87%A6\" data-sr-url